WEBVTT

00:02.136 --> 00:03.468
<i> ["The Ballad Of</i>
     <i> Gilligan's Isle"]</i>

00:03.537 --> 00:05.303
¶ Just sit right back
    and you'll hear a tale ¶

00:05.372 --> 00:08.039
¶ A tale of a fateful trip ¶

00:08.109 --> 00:10.309
¶ That started
    from this tropic port ¶

00:10.377 --> 00:12.544
¶ Aboard this tiny ship ¶

00:12.613 --> 00:15.079
¶ The mate was
     a mighty sailing man ¶

00:15.148 --> 00:17.449
¶ The Skipper brave and sure ¶

00:17.518 --> 00:19.785
¶ Five passengers
      set sail that day ¶

00:19.853 --> 00:22.054
¶ For a three hour tour ¶

00:22.123 --> 00:24.923
¶ A three hour tour ¶

00:24.991 --> 00:26.792
[thunder]

00:26.861 --> 00:29.194
¶ The weather started
     getting rough ¶

00:29.263 --> 00:31.396
¶ The tiny ship was tossed ¶

00:31.464 --> 00:34.199
¶ If not for the courage
    of the fearless crew ¶

00:34.268 --> 00:36.201
¶ The Minnow would be lost ¶

00:36.270 --> 00:38.303
¶ The Minnow would be lost ¶

00:38.372 --> 00:40.405
¶ The ship set ground
     on the shore ¶

00:40.474 --> 00:43.108
¶ Of this uncharted
      desert isle ¶

00:43.177 --> 00:45.777
¶ With Gilligan ¶

00:45.846 --> 00:47.979
¶ The Skipper too ¶

00:48.048 --> 00:52.317
¶ The millionaire and his wife ¶

00:52.386 --> 00:56.788
¶ The movie star and the rest ¶

00:56.857 --> 01:02.094
¶ Are here
     on Gilligan's Isle ¶

01:04.000 --> 01:10.074
